text: Bo Kramer (born 15 Septemper 1998) is a Dutch wheelchair basketball player. She won a bronze medal at the 2016 Summer Paralympics. She played at the 2014 Women's World Wheelchair Basketball Championship. == References == == Other websites == * bo-kramer teamnl.org * THE NETHERLANDS’ BO KRAMER ONE OF RIO 2016’S YOUNGEST PLAYERS , IWBF Oct 13, 2016 Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Paralympic bronze medalists for the Netherlands Category:Dutch wheelchair basketball players
